      <title>共和党的斯特凡尼克在帮助推翻总统后对哈佛保持热度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/stefanik-keeps-heat-on-harvard-after-helping-to-topple-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前学生埃莉斯·斯特凡尼克 (Elise Stefanik) 发表支持唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 总统在 2020 年大选中欺诈的虚假言论后，哈佛大学将这位女议员从顾问委员会中除名，哈佛大学认为这件事已经结束了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/stefanik-keeps-heat-on-harvard-after-helping-to-topple-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗爆炸造成100多人死亡，加剧中东紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/iran-explosions-at-soleimani-grave-kill-more-than-100-and-stoke-mideast-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示，在该国中部地区发动造成100多人死亡的“恐怖”袭击是为了惩罚其对以色列的立场，这是犹太国家与哈马斯之间的战争有可能扩大为更广泛的地区冲突的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/iran-explosions-at-soleimani-grave-kill-more-than-100-and-stoke-mideast-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 16:59:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞拉利昂指控前总统科罗马因挫败政变犯有叛国罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/sierra-leone-charges-ex-president-with-treason-over-foiled-coup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞拉利昂前总统欧内斯特·巴伊·科罗马因涉嫌参与安全部队去年 11 月推翻政府的企图而被指控犯有叛国罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/sierra-leone-charges-ex-president-with-treason-over-foiled-coup</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 16:23:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊总理米佐塔基斯开启 2024 年部长级改组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/greek-premier-mitsotakis-starts-2024-with-ministerial-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯(Kyriakos Mitsotakis)在年初对内阁进行了小规模改革，其中主要变化是在最近体育赛事中发生一系列暴力事件后，公民保护部发生了重大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/greek-premier-mitsotakis-starts-2024-with-ministerial-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 16:11:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rishi Sunak 因庇护申请积压而面临英国监管机构调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/rishi-sunak-faces-uk-watchdog-probe-over-asylum-backlog-claim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相苏纳克声称已清理了英国积压的庇护案件，该国统计监管机构正在对其进行审查，反对派政界人士指责他误导了选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/rishi-sunak-faces-uk-watchdog-probe-over-asylum-backlog-claim</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 15:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
